{"tid":1913303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"質疑遭申訴專員針對　懲教署工會不滿口罩調查非涉轉售","createTime":"2020-03-06T16:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T04:46:58.000Z","uid":105567,"like":29,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"24593329c59620a5781e2f3f43936f8893905e78","tid":1913303,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:12:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512952-20200306.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512952-20200306.htm&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnBURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=7e662a41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512952-20200306.htm&h=8a048dda\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512952-20200306.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n香港懲教署四個協會工會以及退休人員協會發表聲明，對申訴專員主動調查CSI口罩分發、生產及點存，而非如何轉售及挪用，感到非常失望，質疑申訴專員針對懲教署。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指出，多年來口罩存取均由各個政府部門及非政府機構個別處理，懲教署不能干涉，質疑申訴專員執意於抗疫期間針對懲教署，而非調查涉嫌挪用口罩的癥結，感到匪夷所思，又不滿申訴專員以「源頭堵截漏洞」的字眼，形容屬未審先判，感到不明所以。<br />\n<br />\n聲明提及超過1200 名休班退休懲教人員主動於疫情期間，前往羅湖懲教所擔任義工，將口罩產量由過去每月110萬個，增加至每月 250萬個，換來申訴專員無情的針對，令他們抗疫熱情冷卻，表示極度遺憾，希望盡快與申訴專員會面，了解主動調查懲教人員的準則，期望得到一個公平結果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1512952_1_L_20200306234236.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1512952_1_L_20200306234236.jpg&h=a6126481&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60ce907a2a32a73cb5f79a0e32849003af59e766","tid":1913303,"uid":280017,"like":53,"dislike":3,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:16:04.000Z","msg":"此地無銀？<br />\n從唔覺有人針對懲教署職員，反而係針對黑警涉嫌公器私用出售CSI口罩圖利"},{"pid":"d3392c6e66bdb71da429f856e2b1f2e1537314bd","tid":1913303,"uid":25468,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"懲教食左死貓啦 , 係人都知大部分口罩去左邊"},{"pid":"8ec363e1950a7e431f5ed66310c0369cbde35601","tid":1913303,"uid":291865,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:17:46.000Z","msg":"黑狗偷依白狗當災"},{"pid":"0ce5e838aa701d297976d41457124cab9b32944c","tid":1913303,"uid":25468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"60ce907a2a32a73cb5f79a0e32849003af59e766","tid":1913303,"uid":280017,"like":53,"dislike":3,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:16:04.000Z","msg":"此地無銀？<br />\n從唔覺有人針對懲教署職員，反而係針對黑警涉嫌公器私用出售CSI口罩圖利"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:18:56.000Z","msg":"你無睇內文定唔明白內文呀 ?"},{"pid":"c6d62d3e10a652738f8ceea8294e409977981272","tid":1913303,"uid":46966,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁緊加要查啦 你講到咁多休班退休既人努力幫手整<br />\n竟然有撚樣拎去賣 唔查對得住呢班人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec695e9cb1f0adac166384a954b929ff81e1a01a","tid":1913303,"uid":26770,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:21:50.000Z","msg":"懲教都係藍絲狗<br />\n但係人都知係狗隊偷的<br />\n<br />\n班警魔想拉其他人落水"},{"pid":"9cf9c11b99f1f393f09c76a9d19f2e437caf78d4","tid":1913303,"uid":25468,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c6d62d3e10a652738f8ceea8294e409977981272","tid":1913303,"uid":46966,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁緊加要查啦 你講到咁多休班退休既人努力幫手整<br />\n竟然有撚樣拎去賣 唔查對得住呢班人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:25:21.000Z","msg":"而家懲教工會就係屌緊唔調查轉售 , 只查分發情況"},{"pid":"a60ccc5771d743c24edcad8193564ef9d1871565","tid":1913303,"uid":193364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"24593329c59620